[7] French Antilles and Guiana
Date: 28 Apr - 4 May 2014
Source: InVS Point Epidemiologique No. 17 [in French, trans. Mod.TY, edited]
http://www.invs.sante.fr/fr/content/download/88007/323031/version/64/file/pe_chikungunya_antilles_070514.pdf


Cases since the beginning of the outbreak in December 2013:
- St. Martin: (susp.) 3210 cases; Deaths 3; Stable.
- St. Barthelemy: (susp.) 490 cases; Low to decreasing slightly.
- Martinique: (susp.) 21 820; Deaths 3; Increasing.
- Guadeloupe: (susp.) 10 600 cases; Deaths 1; Increasing.
- French Guiana: (probable or confirmed) 81 cases with 57 locally acquired; Slightly increasing, with a new cluster in Cayenne.

